tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ProteinInfo (
  protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protein_name VARCHAR(255),
  protein_sequence TEXT,
  molecular_weight FLOAT,
  isoelectric_point FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_id INT,
    date DATE,
    method VARCHAR(50),
    result TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (protein_id) REFERENCES proteins(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Proteins (
  protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protein_name VARCHAR(255),
  gene_name VARCHAR(255),
  molecular_weight DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE Peptides (
  peptide_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  peptide_sequence VARCHAR(255),
  protein_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (protein_id) REFERENCES Proteins(protein_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Experiments (
  experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
  experiment_date DATE,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE Measurements (
  measurement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT,
  peptide_id INT,
  intensity DECIMAL,
  retention_time DECIMAL,
  FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES Experiments(experiment_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (peptide_id) REFERENCES Peptides(peptide_id)
)
